## 赛博朋克设计原则

### 1. 暗色为主的配色方案

- **主背景**：`bg-cyber-gray-900` (#0a0a0a)
- **卡片/面板**：`bg-cyber-gray-800` (#1a1a1a) 或 `bg-cyber-gray-700` (#2a2a2a)
- **边框**：`border-cyber-gray-600` (#404040)

### 2. 霓虹发光效果

使用 CSS `box-shadow` 和 `text-shadow` 实现：

```css
/* 霓虹按钮 */
.cyber-neon-button {
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 5px currentColor,
    0 0 10px currentColor,
    0 0 15px currentColor,
    0 0 20px currentColor;
}

/* 霓虹文本 */
.cyber-neon-text {
  text-shadow:
    0 0 5px currentColor,
    0 0 10px currentColor,
    0 0 15px currentColor;
}
```

### 3. 渐变与光效

- **主要渐变**：`bg-gradient-to-r from-cyber-brand-500 to-cyber-neon-cyan`
- **背景渐变**：`bg-gradient-to-br from-cyber-gray-900 to-cyber-brand-50`
- **边框渐变**：`border-gradient` 使用品牌色到霓虹色

### 4. 几何线条与网格

- 使用细线条 (1px) 构建科技感网格
- 对角线、六边形等几何形状装饰
- 数字化风格的分割线

## 组件设计规范

### 按钮系统

```css
/* 主要按钮 - 霓虹风格 */
.btn-primary {
  @apply bg-cyber-brand-500 text-white px-6 py-3;
  @apply border border-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply hover:bg-transparent hover:text-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply transition-all duration-300;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(51, 102, 255, 0.3);
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 5px #3366FF,
    0 0 10px #3366FF,
    0 0 15px #3366FF;
}

/* 次要按钮 - 轮廓风格 */
.btn-secondary {
  @apply bg-transparent text-cyber-gray-300;
  @apply border border-cyber-gray-600;
  @apply hover:border-cyber-brand-500 hover:text-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply transition-all duration-300;
}

/* 危险按钮 - 霓虹红 */
.btn-danger {
  @apply bg-red-600 text-white;
  @apply hover:bg-transparent hover:text-red-400;
  @apply border border-red-600 hover:border-red-400;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
}
```

### 输入框系统

```css
.cyber-input {
  @apply bg-cyber-gray-800 text-cyber-gray-200;
  @apply border border-cyber-gray-600;
  @apply focus:border-cyber-brand-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply transition-all duration-300;
}

.cyber-input:focus {
  box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(51, 102, 255, 0.5);
}
```

### 卡片系统

```css
.cyber-card {
  @apply bg-cyber-gray-800 border border-cyber-gray-600;
  @apply rounded-lg p-6;
  @apply hover:border-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply transition-all duration-300;
}

.cyber-card-neon {
  @apply cyber-card;
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 10px rgba(51, 102, 255, 0.1),
    inset 0 0 10px rgba(51, 102, 255, 0.05);
}
```

### 导航与链接

```css
.cyber-nav-link {
  @apply text-cyber-gray-300 hover:text-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply transition-colors duration-300;
  @apply relative;
}

.cyber-nav-link::after {
  content: '';
  @apply absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-0.5;
  @apply bg-cyber-brand-500 transition-all duration-300;
}

.cyber-nav-link:hover::after {
  @apply w-full;
  box-shadow: 0 0 5px #3366FF;
}
```

## 文本层次系统

### 标题

- **H1**: `text-4xl font-bold text-cyber-gray-100` + 霓虹效果
- **H2**: `text-3xl font-semibold text-cyber-gray-200`
- **H3**: `text-2xl font-medium text-cyber-brand-500`
- **H4**: `text-xl font-medium text-cyber-gray-300`

### 正文

- **主要文本**: `text-cyber-gray-300` (满足AA标准对比度4.7:1)
- **次要文本**: `text-cyber-gray-500`
- **标注文本**: `text-cyber-gray-400`

### 特殊文本

- **强调文本**: `text-cyber-brand-500` + 霓虹效果
- **代码文本**: `font-mono text-cyber-neon-green bg-cyber-gray-800`
- **链接文本**: `text-cyber-brand-500 hover:text-cyber-brand-600`

## 动画与交互

### 过渡效果

```css
.cyber-transition {
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

.cyber-glow-animate {
  animation: cyberGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes cyberGlow {
  from { box-shadow: 0 0 5px currentColor; }
  to { box-shadow: 0 0 20px currentColor; }
}
```

### 悬浮效果

- 卡片悬浮：轻微上升 + 边框发光
- 按钮悬浮：背景透明化 + 边框发光
- 文本悬浮：颜色渐变 + 文本发光

