## 可访问性实现

### 焦点指示器

```css
.cyber-focus {
  @apply focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cyber-brand-500;
  @apply focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-cyber-gray-900;
}
```

### 高对比模式

```css
@media (prefers-contrast: high) {
  .cyber-text { @apply text-white; }
  .cyber-bg { @apply bg-black; }
  .cyber-border { @apply border-white; }
}
```

### 减少动画选项

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .cyber-glow-animate { animation: none; }
  .cyber-transition { transition: none; }
}
```

